author: Samantha Highfill
title: Celebrities remember Trayvon Martin on the fifth anniversary of his death
text:
Email C Flanigan/FilmMagic; Dimitrios Kambouris/Getty Images; Jason LaVeris/FilmMagic 
On February 26, 2012, 17-year-old Trayvon Martin was fatally shot by George Zimmerman in Sanford, Florida. Although Zimmerman was not initially charged with a crime, the case garnered national media attention, which led to Zimmerman being tried for second degree murder before he was later acquitted. 
On the fifth anniversary of Martinâ€™s death, celebrities have taken to social media to pay their respects.
